title: Phish - 1991/10/13:  North Shore Surf Club - Olympia, WA  [SBD](
description:
This is from etree.org (filename:ph91-10-13).  Once again, I've just tagged all the files.  On disc 2, there is filler from 1991/07/19, which you can easily delete or separate if you so choose.

This is another one of the best Phish shows ever, a heavily circulated tape from the early days (the 90's).  This Runaway Jim is my absolute favorite, and has turned at least one indifferent listener into a stone-cold Phish junkie....which allowed them to discover the Dead, next Zappa.  (I'm not referring to myself, but to a friend of mine).
